	.txt_title2{
		
		text-shadow: 
			-1px -1px 0 black, 1px -1px 0 black, -1px 1px 0 black, 1px 1px 0 black,
				2px 2px 3px black, 
			1px 0px 0px #FF6602, 0px 1px 0px #FF6602, 2px 1px 0px #FF6602, 1px 2px 0px #FF6602, 3px 2px 0px #FF6602, 2px 3px 0px #FF6602, 4px 3px 0px #FF6602, 3px 4px 0px #FF6602, 5px 4px 0px #FF6602,

			-1px 2px 0 black, 0 3px 0 black, 1px 4px 0 black, 2px 5px 0px black,
			2px -1px 0 black, 3px 0 0 black, 4px 1px 0 black, 5px 2px 0px black, 6px 3px 0 black, 7px 4px 0 black,
				2px 2px 4px black;
	
	}
	
	.txt_animatedTitle {
	
		text-shadow: 
			-1px -1px 0 black,
			1px -1px 0 black,
			-1px 1px 0 black,
			1px 1px 0 black,
			2px 2px 3px #000000;
			
		animation: an_shake .1s linear infinite;
	}
	
	.menuSelection{
		text-shadow: 
			-1px -1px 0 black, 1px -1px 0 black, -1px 1px 0 black, 1px 1px 0 black,
			2px 2px 3px #000000;
		cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/IMG_CURSOR_HAND.png"), auto !important;
		
		transition: all .3s ease;
			
	}
	
	/*for techy intro, download and cute text*/
	.txt_advocute{
	
		/*display: inline !important;
 		background: teal !important;*/
 		
 		text-shadow: 
			-1px -1px 0 black, 1px -1px 0 black, -1px 1px 0 black, 1px 1px 0 blue;
	
	}
	
	.menuSelection:active{
		transform: translate(0px, 5px);
		-webkit-transform: translate(0px, 5px);
		box-shadow: 0px 1px 0px 0px;
	}
	
	.menuSelection:hover{
		transform: scale(1.2) perspective(1px);
	}
	
	.btn_element_animated{
		cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/IMG_CURSOR_HAND.png"), auto !important;
		transition: all .3s ease;
	}
	.btn_element_animated:hover{
		transform: scale(1.2) perspective(1px);
	}
	
	
	.btn_element, .fishlet, .hrefClassic{
		cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/IMG_CURSOR_HAND.png"), auto !important;
	}
	
	.container{
		cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/IMG_CURSOR_DEFAULT.png"), auto !important;
	}
	
	/*manage default ahref's...*/
	a{
		cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/IMG_CURSOR_HAND.png"), auto !important;
		transition: all .3s ease;
	}
	a:hover{
		transform: scale(2) !important;
		color: grey !important;
	}
	
	/*shaking elements -- NOTE: COMMENT BACK IN WHEN DONE BUILDING THIS*/
	.shaking{
		animation: an_shake .1s linear infinite;
	}
	
	/*talking and speech bubbles (anime font)*/
	.speech {
  		display: inline;
  		background: white;
  		box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px black;
	}
	
	.yelling{
		 display: inline;
  		background: white;
  		box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px black;
  		animation: an_shake .1s linear infinite;
	}
	
	/*SITE page (inspection cursors and buttons...)*/
	.siteInspect{
		/*cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/ICO_CURSOR_INSPECT_LOOK_SML.png"), auto !important;*/
		cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/IMG_CURSOR_MAGNIFY_EXAMINE.png"), auto !important;
		transition: all .3s ease;
		
	}
	.siteInspect:hover{
		transform: scale(1.4) !important;
	}
	/*inspect without the hover animation*/
	.siteInspectBasic{
		cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/IMG_CURSOR_MAGNIFY_EXAMINE.png"), auto !important;
	}
	/*site inspection for classic hyperlinks*/
	.siteInspectHref{
		color: blue !important;;
		text-decoration: underline;
		cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/IMG_CURSOR_MAGNIFY_EXAMINE.png"), auto !important;
		transition: all .3s ease;
	}
	.siteInspectHref:hover{
		transform: scale(1.4) !important;
	}
	
	/*SITE PAGE inspection messages*/
	.inspectionMessage{
		display: inline;
  		background: white;
  		box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px black;
  		/*transform: rotate(-4.5deg) !important;*/
  		cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/IMG_CURSOR_DEFAULT.png"), auto !important;
  		
  		/*display: flex;
  		align-items: center !important;
  		justify-content: center !important;*/
  		/*text-align: center;*/
	}
	/*part of the above, the countdown*/
	.inspectionMessageCountdown{
		display: inline;
  		background: #FFFF99;
  		box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px black;
  		cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/IMG_CURSOR_DEFAULT.png"), auto !important;
  		animation: an_countdown 1s ease-out infinite;
	}
	
	.inspectionMessageButton{
		display: inline;
  		background: black;
  		color: white !important;
  		padding: 10px;
		cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/IMG_CURSOR_HAND.png"), auto !important;
		/*line-height: 30px;*/
	}
	
	/*items obtained screen (zelda like)*/
	.itemObtainedMessage{
		display: inline;
  		background: black;
  		box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px black;
	}
	
	
	/*classic buttons*/
	.hrefClassic{
		color: blue !important;;
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	.hrefClassic:visited{
		color: purple;
	}
	.hrefClassic:hover{
		animation: an_shake .1s linear infinite;
	}
	
	/*padding around the hype container*/
	#index_hype_container{

		top: 5%;
		
		min-width: 640px;
		min-height: 960px;
	}
	
	
	@keyframes an_shake {
		0% { transform: translate(1px, 1px) rotate(0deg); }
		10% { transform: translate(-1px, -2px) rotate(-1deg); }
		20% { transform: translate(-3px, 0px) rotate(1deg); }
		30% { transform: translate(3px, 2px) rotate(0deg); }
    	40% { transform: translate(1px, -1px) rotate(1deg); }
    	50% { transform: translate(-1px, 2px) rotate(-1deg); }
    	60% { transform: translate(-3px, 1px) rotate(0deg); }
    	70% { transform: translate(3px, 1px) rotate(-1deg); }
    	80% { transform: translate(-1px, -1px) rotate(1deg); }
    	90% { transform: translate(1px, 2px) rotate(0deg); }
    	100% { transform: translate(1px, -2px) rotate(-1deg); }
	}
	
	@keyframes an_countdown{
		0%   { background: red; }
		50%  { background: yellow; }
		100% { background: red; }
	}
